org.pvg.plasmagraph.models

Class DataSetModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pvg.plasmagraph.models.DataSetModel

  • public class DataSetModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Model for the modification of PlasmaGraph's data sets. Manipulates both the data sets that will be used in the graphs as well as the HeaderDataView itself.
    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group
